CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1774624292
OL,3,CFamily tribute as murder investigation
OL,4,Cunderway in Nottinghamshire
OL,6,FThe statement reads: "It is with
OL,7,Fprofound sorrow that we announce the
OL,8,Fpassing of Orinta Narbutaite, a
OL,9,Fcherished member of our community
OL,10,Fwhose kindness, dignity, and warmth
OL,11,Fleft a lasting impression on all who
OL,12,Fknew her.
OL,14,F"Orinta will be remembered not only
OL,15,Ffor her compassionate nature and quiet
OL,16,Fstrength, but also for the genuine
OL,17,Fcare and respect she showed to others.
OL,26,@nD@VOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1774624292
OL,3,CFamily tribute as murder investigation
OL,4,Cunderway in Nottinghamshire
OL,6,F"She had a remarkable ability to offer
OL,7,Fcomfort and support and her presence
OL,8,Fbrought a sense of calm and
OL,9,Freassurance to those around her.
OL,11,F"Above all, Orinta was a devoted and
OL,12,Floving mother to her daughter, whom
OL,13,Fshe cherished deeply. Her love,
OL,14,Fguidance, and dedication as a parent
OL,15,Fwill remain a lasting part of her
OL,16,Flegacy.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1774624292
OL,3,CFamily tribute as murder investigation
OL,4,Cunderway in Nottinghamshire
OL,6,F"Orinta Narbutaite will be deeply
OL,7,Fmissed and forever remembered. Her
OL,8,Fmemory will continue to live on in the
OL,9,Fhearts of all who had the privilege of
OL,10,Fknowing her."
OL,12,FAn investigation was launched
OL,13,Ffollowing the discovery.
OL,15,FDonatas Noreika, of Main Street,
OL,16,FMilton, and Arturas Karvelis, of Broad
OL,17,FStreet, Parkgate, Rotherham - who is
OL,18,Falso known within the community as
OL,19,FArturas Bockus - were charged with
OL,20,Fconspiring to prevent the lawful and
OL,21,Fdecent burial of a body.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@MO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
