FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1774624292
OL,3,CFamily tribute as murder investigation
OL,4,Cunderway in Nottinghamshire
OL,6,FNoreika, aged 37, and Karvelis, aged
OL,7,F45, have since been remanded in
OL,8,Fcustody and are next due to appear in
OL,9,FNottingham Crown Court on Monday,
OL,10,FApril 20.
OL,12,FDetective Inspector Matt Scott, of
OL,13,FNottinghamshire Police, said: "Our
OL,14,Fthoughts remain with Orinta's family
OL,15,Fand friends, who have asked for
OL,16,Fprivacy at what must be an extremely
OL,17,Fdifficult time.
OL,26,@uD@_OU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
